//Mediastinal vessels - Pulmonary arteries

Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 09 of Cardio MRI
And I select 'Finding' radio button
And I select 'Mediastinal vessels' from the dropdown menu

When I select 'Pulmonary arteries' radio button
Then 'Thrombus' checkbox is enabled

And 'Central pulmonary artery diameter' input field is enabled

And 'Acute pulmonary embolism' radio button is enabled
And 'Chronic pulmonary embolism' radio button is enabled
And 'Pulmonary hypertension' radio button is enabled


When I select 'Thrombus' checkbox
Then 'Centralis' checkbox is enabled
And 'Dextra' checkbox is enabled
And 'Right, segmental' checkbox is enabled
And 'Sinistra' checkbox is enabled
And 'Left, segmental' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Aorta descendens' checkbox
Then 'Max. diameter' input field is enabled

When I select 'Acute pulmonary embolism' radio button
Then 'Suspicion of' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Chronic pulmonary embolism' radio button
Then 'Suspicion of' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Pulmonary hypertension' radio button
Then 'Suspicion of' checkbox is enabled
